data.description: NO EXPENSE SPARED IN THIS COMPLETE RENOVATION!!! ALL NEW roof, HVAC, plumbing, electrical, tankless hot water heater, windows, doors, flooring, tile, cabinets, appliances and SO MUCH MORE! Not only does this house sit on nearly 5 acres, it was brought down to the studs and is an absolute show stopper!!! Step inside to an open floor plan with a light and airy feel thanks to the brand new oversized windows. LVP flooring and tile make up the living room floors with the kitchen being completely decked out with new appliances, granite counters, and tile backsplash. Spacious living room and dining area all lit with brand new light fixtures. A hall bath off of the foyer for guests, with the primary bath being accessed through the hall or master suite. Granite counter tops, tile shower, gorgeous light fixtures all await you in this ideal and practical bathroom. Bedrooms are all a generous size! A 2 car garage with brand new garage doors. More things to love: CAT5 ethernet cables to every room, 11 trees were cut down giving the open feel to the land, fence for pets, and renovated deck, and no restrictions on this beautiful piece of land! Truly a modern paradise with a "out in the country" feel!!!  Contact your trusted realtor or myself for a showing today!!!
